  <section class="section-quiz" data-depth="1" data-element-type="section-quiz">
    <h3 data-type="title">Section Quiz</h3>
    <div data-element-type="section-quiz" data-type="exercise">
      <div data-type="problem">
        <p>Which of the following best describes sociology as a subject?</p>
        <ol type="a">
          <li>The study of individual behavior</li>
          <li>The study of cultures</li>
          <li>The study of society and social interaction</li>
          <li>The study of economics</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div data-label="" data-type="solution">
        <div data-type="title">Answers</div>
        <p>C</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div data-element-type="section-quiz" data-type="exercise">
      <div data-type="problem">
        <p>C. Wright Mills once said that sociologists need to develop a sociological __________ to study how society affects individuals.</p>
        <ol type="a">
          <li>culture</li>
          <li>imagination</li>
          <li>method</li>
          <li>tool</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div data-label="" data-type="solution">
        <div data-type="title">Answers</div>
        <p>B</p>
      </div>
    </div>
